&Control
Calculation PAD
Log_file graphene_4x7_PAD.log
Console_log false
Output_file graphene_4x7_PAD.hdf5
/
&Atomic-wfn
Potential_file /path/to/Atomic_potentials.hdf5
/
&Radial-grid 3
0.0025 40
0.005  40
0.01   40000
/
&Phase-shift
Skip_points 10
Calc_points 10
/
&PAD
Input_file graphene_4x7.hdf5
E_min -2
E_max 2
E_pixel 0.05
dE 0.1
Initial_state AO
Final_state Calc
Polarization Linear
Theta 90
Phi 0
Atomic_orbitals_file /path/to/PAO_and_AO_after_opt.hdf5
Extend 5 5 5 5
! Output_data Band
/
